---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { CONTACT_EMAIL, SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="landing">
			<section class="hero">
				<p class="hero__eyebrow">AI Developer Blog</p>
				<h1>{SITE_TITLE}</h1>
				<p class="hero__description">
					AI 개발자 김민상 블로그입니다. 실험에서 얻은 통찰, 제품 적용 경험, 그리고 함께 성장하는 개발 노트를 아카이브합니다.
				</p>
				<div class="hero__actions">
					<a class="button button--primary" href="/blog">블로그 읽기</a>
					<a class="button button--ghost" href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>메일 보내기</a>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="highlights">
				<h2>What you'll find here</h2>
				<div class="highlight-grid">
					<article class="card">
						<h3>LLM &amp; 생성형 AI</h3>
						<p>프롬프트 엔지니어링, 파인튜닝, 멀티모달 모델 실험기를 기록합니다.</p>
					</article>
					<article class="card">
						<h3>MLOps &amp; 프로덕션</h3>
						<p>실제 서비스에 적용하며 겪은 운영 전략과 자동화 파이프라인을 공유합니다.</p>
					</article>
					<article class="card">
						<h3>학습 노트</h3>
						<p>논문 리뷰와 사이드 프로젝트 진행 과정을 꾸준히 정리합니다.</p>
					</article>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="cta">
				<h2>Let's collaborate</h2>
				<p>{SITE_DESCRIPTION}</p>
				<a class="button button--primary" href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>프로젝트 제안하기</a>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.landing {
		width: min(960px, calc(100% - 2em));
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 4em 0 5em;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 4em;
	}
	.hero {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5em;
		padding: 3.5em 3em;
		border-radius: 24px;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(35, 55, 255, 0.08), rgba(29, 78, 216, 0.12));
		box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(15, 18, 25, 0.08);
	}
	.hero__eyebrow {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.9em;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: rgba(15, 18, 25, 0.6);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.2em;
	}
	.hero h1 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
		line-height: 1.1;
		color: rgb(var(--black));
	}
	.hero__description {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.1em;
		color: rgba(15, 18, 25, 0.75);
		max-width: 60ch;
	}
	.hero__actions {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.75em;
	}
	.button {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 0.75em 1.6em;
		border-radius: 999px;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
	}
	.button--primary {
		background: var(--accent);
		color: white;
		box-shadow: 0 18px 30px rgba(35, 55, 255, 0.18);
	}
	.button--primary:hover {
		background: var(--accent-dark);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 22px 36px rgba(35, 55, 255, 0.25);
	}
	.button--ghost {
		background: white;
		color: var(--accent);
		border: 1px solid rgba(35, 55, 255, 0.2);
	}
	.button--ghost:hover {
		background: rgba(35, 55, 255, 0.08);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}
	.highlights {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2em;
	}
	.highlights h2 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		color: rgb(var(--black));
	}
	.highlight-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5em;
	}
	.card {
		padding: 1.75em;
		border-radius: 18px;
		background: white;
		box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(15, 18, 25, 0.05);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.75em;
	}
	.card h3 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
	}
	.card p {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		color: rgba(15, 18, 25, 0.7);
	}
	.cta {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 3em;
		border-radius: 22px;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(35, 55, 255, 0.12), rgba(15, 18, 25, 0.08));
		box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(15, 18, 25, 0.08);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1em;
		align-items: center;
	}
	.cta h2 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.9rem;
	}
	.cta p {
		margin: 0;
		max-width: 60ch;
		color: rgba(15, 18, 25, 0.75);
	}
	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.hero {
			padding: 2.5em 1.75em;
		}
		.cta {
			padding: 2.5em 1.5em;
		}
	}
</style>
